5#include "src/compiler/turboshaft/representations.h"

7namespace v8::internal::compiler::turboshaft {
8
9std::ostream& operator<<(std::ostream& os, MaybeRegisterRepresentation rep) {
10 switch (rep) {
11 case MaybeRegisterRepresentation::Word32():
12 return os << "Word32";
13 case MaybeRegisterRepresentation::Word64():
14 return os << "Word64";
15 case MaybeRegisterRepresentation::Float32():
16 return os << "Float32";
17 case MaybeRegisterRepresentation::Float64():
18 return os << "Float64";
19 case MaybeRegisterRepresentation::Tagged():
20 return os << "Tagged";
21 case MaybeRegisterRepresentation::Compressed():
22 return os << "Compressed";
23 case MaybeRegisterRepresentation::Simd128():
24 return os << "Simd128";
25 case MaybeRegisterRepresentation::Simd256():
26 return os << "Simd256";
27 case MaybeRegisterRepresentation::None():
28 return os << "None";
29 }
30}
31
32std::ostream& operator<<(std::ostream& os, MemoryRepresentation rep) {
33 switch (rep) {
34 case MemoryRepresentation::Int8():
35 return os << "Int8";
36 case MemoryRepresentation::Uint8():
37 return os << "Uint8";
38 case MemoryRepresentation::Int16():
39 return os << "Int16";
40 case MemoryRepresentation::Uint16():
41 return os << "Uint16";
42 case MemoryRepresentation::Int32():
43 return os << "Int32";
44 case MemoryRepresentation::Uint32():
45 return os << "Uint32";
46 case MemoryRepresentation::Int64():
47 return os << "Int64";
48 case MemoryRepresentation::Uint64():
49 return os << "Uint64";
50 case MemoryRepresentation::Float32():
51 return os << "Float32";
52 case MemoryRepresentation::Float64():
53 return os << "Float64";
54 case MemoryRepresentation::AnyTagged():
55 return os << "AnyTagged";
56 case MemoryRepresentation::TaggedPointer():
57 return os << "TaggedPointer";
58 case MemoryRepresentation::TaggedSigned():
59 return os << "TaggedSigned";
60 case MemoryRepresentation::ProtectedPointer():
61 return os << "ProtectedPointer";
62 case MemoryRepresentation::IndirectPointer():
63 return os << "IndirectPointer";
64 case MemoryRepresentation::SandboxedPointer():
65 return os << "SandboxedPointer";
66 case MemoryRepresentation::Simd128():
67 return os << "Simd128";
68 case MemoryRepresentation::Simd256():
69 return os << "Simd256";
70 }
71}
